701231f-a.title: Bronx: Havemeyer Avenue - Watson Avenue
701231f-a.text:
Havemeyer Ave., east side, north from Watson Ave. The first house
is Hoffman's Casino, No. 1118,at the S.E. corner of Haviland Ave.
July 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
